org.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM projects LEFT OUTER JOIN custom_values AS cf_3 ON cf_3.customized_type = 'Project' AND cf_3.customized_id = projects.id AND cf_3.custom_field_id = 3 AND 1 = 1 AND cf_3.value <> '' AND cf_3.id = (SELECT MAX(cf_3_2.id) FROM custom_values AS cf_3_2 WHERE cf_3_2.customized_type = cf_3.customized_type AND cf_3_2.customized_id = cf_3.customized_id AND cf_3_2.custom_field_id = cf_3.custom_field_id) WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND projects.status IN ('1')
